cff-version: 1.2.0
title: The Real Middle
message: >-
  If you use this software or its data visualizations, please cite it
  using the metadata from this file.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Sri Raman
    given-names: Varna
    alias: Varnasr
repository-code: https://github.com/Varnasr/The-Real-Middle
url: https://impactmojo.in
abstract: >-
  An interactive tool helping Indian users discover their actual economic
  position within India's income distribution. Addresses the common
  misconception where upper-income earners self-identify as "middle class"
  through income calculators, budget simulations, healthcare and education
  cost analysis, rural vs urban comparisons, and poverty cycle exploration.
keywords:
  - income-inequality
  - india
  - economic-position
  - middle-class
  - data-visualization
  - react
license: MIT
